</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp40890272">
<problem id="fs-idp40890528">
<para id="fs-idp40890784">Hvað af eftirfarandi táknar fæstar
sameindir?</para>
<para id="fs-idp40891168">(a) 20,0 g af H<sub>2</sub>O (18,02 g/mól)</para>
<para id="fs-idp40891936">(b) 77,0 g af CH<sub>4</sub> (16,06 g/mól)</para>
<para id="fs-idp40892704">(c) 68,0 g af C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>6</sub> (42,08
